<br>
Pets you summon while holding the proper pet focus item will be larger with their best attribute enhanced a great deal but all of their attributes get taken up a notch. The Temple of Ro focus items work on all elemental pets of the appropriate type from level 4 to 49, they do not work on the 50+ pets or on monster pets. And remember it's:<br>
<br>
Broom of Trilon for Air pets<br>
Shovel of Ponz for Earth pets<br>
Torch of Alna for Fire pets<br>
Stein of Ulissa for Water pets<br>
<br>
There are currently no known monster pet focii in the game, in the past there were rumors of various items being monster pet focii but so far they have just been rumors and they didn't work out. <p><br>
